verbose_text: Additionally, a large set of genes implicated in mitogen activated protein kinase (MAPK), vascular endothelial growth factor (VEGF), protein kinase C (PKC)-mitogen-activated protein kinase (MEK), phosphatidylinositol 3-kinase (PI3K)-protein kinase B (AKT), as well as the WNT signaling pathway were mediated by the dysregulated miRNAs (XREF_FIG; pathway ID, 05200 for XREF_FIG).
